M34WQ (with built-in KVM).  I've got two attachments (one from my 
dekstop through HDMI and USB-B and the other through USB-C attached to 
my laptop).  I can confirm that changing the value of 0x60 to the 
opposing value switches the KVM source (including keyboard/mouse/etc).

Please let me know if you need any additional information...

